1. *Zatvori* ga u sobi (Close him in the room).
2. *Zatvorio* je knjigu (He closed the book).
3. *Zatvorena* vrata (Closed doors).
4. On je *zatvorio* svoje srce (He closed his heart).
5. Ona je *zatvorila* sve prozore (She closed all the windows).
6. *Zatvaranje* vrata (Closing the doors).
7. On je *zatvorio* oƒçi (He closed his eyes).
8. Ona je *zatvarala* knjigu (She was closing the book).
9. *Zatvori* vrata (Close the doors).
10. Oni su *zatvorili* knjigu (They closed the book).